  "description": "Taiko handles the deep boom of an 80s stadium kick. Tabla high tones simulate the sharp snare crack drenched in gated reverb. A tight conga sixteenth-note pattern weaves through the grid like the hi-hat track on an LM-1. This is the drum sound of Toto and Depeche Mode co-writing.",
